{"tid":2157809,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"莫迪稱印度主權至高無上　任何人敢瞧一眼將以軍隊回應   誓言要打造更強大的軍隊","createTime":"2020-08-15T09:35:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T09:42:17.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"24c68bdf81db42fadc7e2d938fce512f6526240d","tid":2157809,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T09:35:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543903-20200815.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543903-20200815.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8SvUjXV925tPaxuyg6D%2B4Js%3D&h=c7ec97b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543903-20200815.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ecfd6da8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543903-20200815.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n印度總理莫迪強調，印度的主權至高無上，又誓言要打造更強大的軍隊。<br />\n<br />\n莫迪發表獨立日演說，不點名提到印度與中國及巴基斯坦在邊界對峙。莫迪說，任何人敢對印度主權瞧一眼，印度軍方就會用自己的語言回應，強調軍隊有能力做到，每個人都在拉達克地區見到這個情況，意指中印軍隊6月在拉達克地區的衝突。<br />\n<br />\n莫迪說，印度在戰鬥中無失去任何土地，又說與鄰國的關係取決於安全與信任，只有彼此尊重，雙方關係才會溫暖。<br />\n<br />\n莫迪同時指出，將會打造一支140萬人的軍隊，並要在國防生產事業中自力更生，但目前最重要的工作，是讓印度擺脫新型肺炎疫情引發的危機。"},{"pid":"c77e7d6715a9326173b29ada452b3a56eba16764","tid":2157809,"uid":105340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T09:39:54.000Z","msg":"領土問題 不容商討<br />\nHIT OR NO HIT , THERE IS NO DEAL"},{"pid":"586a48daeeaed4345b07205d90f50332651b1da9","tid":2157809,"uid":252142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T09:41:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b00cc6c2c405f9270847d690e177ec14095dc51","tid":2157809,"uid":295230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T09:42:17.000Z","msg":"莫迪呀莫迪"}]}